Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:16.12,JP-米,,533,0,0,,We're singing at a \Nbaseball stadium? I'm in
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:20.21,JP-果,,0,0,0,,大きな会場でやれる機会なんて滅多にないし
